OL,3,CProtesters gather to rally against
OL,4,Cplans to close care home
OL,6,FITV News Central's Peter Bearne
OL,7,Freports.
OL,9,FProtesters in Belper have gathered
OL,10,Fover plans to save a Derbyshire County
OL,11,FCouncil care home in Belper.
OL,13,FThe rally started on Saturday morning
OL,14,Foutside the Ada Belfield Centre, on
OL,15,FDerwent Street, before proceeding to
OL,16,Fthe Strutts Community Centre, on Derby
OL,17,FRoad, where campaigners met
OL,18,Fcouncillors, council officers and Mid
OL,19,FDerbyshire MP Jonathan Davies at
OL,20,Fmidday.
