OL,3,CProtesters gather to rally against
OL,4,Cplans to close care home
OL,6,FThe Ada Bellfield care home is one of
OL,7,Fthree earmarked for a proposed sale or
OL,8,Fclosure after eight others have been
OL,9,Fselected to close.
OL,11,FThe council's consultation states that
OL,12,Fthe only two options are to "sell as a
OL,13,Fgoing concern" which would mean taking
OL,14,Fthe care home out of public ownership,
OL,15,For selling the care home as an empty
OL,16,Fbuilding.
OL,18,FThe consultation, to determine the
OL,19,Ffuture of Ada Bellfield opened on the
OL,20,F2nd of December last year and closed
OL,21,Fon the 12th of January.
