OL,6,FThe privatisation plans comes after
OL,7,Fthe Derbyshire County Council
OL,8,Fprojected a #39 million budget deficit
OL,9,Ffor this financial year.
OL,11,FThey say reduced government funding,
OL,12,Fthe pandemic, inflation, higher prices
OL,13,Fand rising costs, as well as the
OL,14,Fgrowing demand for adults' and
OL,15,Fchildren's social care services, are
OL,16,Fto blame.
OL,18,FThe campaign group, Belper Together
OL,19,Fare calling for the plans to be
OL,20,Freconsidered and were formed to stop
OL,21,Fthe care home being sold off or closed.
