OL,6,FThe award-winning care home opened in
OL,7,F2020 at a cost of over #11 million.
OL,9,FIt currently accommodates 40 residents
OL,10,Fand offers services for people with
OL,11,Fdementia, physical disabilities and
OL,12,Fsensory impairments.
OL,14,FThe care home is located on the former
OL,15,FThornton's factory in a UNESCO World
OL,16,FHeritage site.
OL,18,FA petition to save the care home
OL,19,Fstarted by Ben Bellamy, Councillor for
OL,20,FBelper North has already gained just
OL,21,Funder 3 and a half thousand signatures.
