OL,6,FDerbyshire County Council's cabinet
OL,7,Fmember for adult care Councillor
OL,8,FNatalie Hoy said: "We are seeing a
OL,9,Fcontinued decline in people choosing
OL,10,Fto go into a traditional residential
OL,11,Fcare setting, instead people are
OL,12,Fwanting and are choosing to live
OL,13,Findependently in their own homes for
OL,14,Fas long as possible.
