OL,6,F"Evidence shows fewer people are
OL,7,Fchoosing, and will choose, to live in
OL,8,Fa traditional residential care
OL,9,Fsetting, such as Ada Belfield. Because
OL,10,Fpeople are choosing to stay at home
OL,11,Ffor as long as possible, when they
OL,12,Fenter care settings they have more
OL,13,Facute needs which means they need
OL,14,Fnursing care which we're not legally
OL,15,Fallowed to provide.
